Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:04.48,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,Yaga, what is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:10.95,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,I know man-made cursed corpses can act \Nmore autonomously than other forms of manipulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:15.87,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,but they're always powered \Nby cursed energy from the sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:20.38,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,Yet that thing is sustaining \Nitself on its own cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:25.59,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,The higher-ups are preparing \Nto formally designate you as special grade
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:28.97,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,and place you in indefinite detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:33.81,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,Because if you can intentionally create that thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:37.68,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,you could easily have your own army.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.27,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,Answer me, Yaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:47.03,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,164,,Do you truly not know how that thing was made?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:50.70,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:53.41,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,Masamichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:56.37,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,Everyone's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:57.95,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,They say you seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:00:59.66,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Is that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.92,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,So I told them all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:06.92,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,If you're feeling down, \Nwe just have to cheer you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.55,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:12.72,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,I'm a genius, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.64,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:19.60,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Takeru, I'm sorry, but I won't be able \Nto come home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:22.35,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Please let the others know, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.19,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,Another work trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:27.03,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Yeah. It'll be a long one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.28,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Don't worry. {It'll be all right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:31.61,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,This forest is protected by {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:35.45,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Your mom will come see you again, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.87,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,You'll be all right without me. {Even if I'm not around, it'll be all right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.50,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,Masamichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.84,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,It'll be lonely without you, Masamichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.26,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Kusakabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.47,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,0,,Don't go telling anyone I helped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.77,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,0,,You were captured to lure Yaga{**-san} out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.15,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,0,,And I owe him a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.86,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,0,,Go on, get!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.74,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,You're sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.70,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,This thing is not your nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.12,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,It's just something \Nwith your nephew's information.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:23.79,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,You're trying to say people can't live in the present\Nif they stay hung up on the dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:31.59,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,Still, my little sister \Ncan no longer live without Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:39.60,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,Masamichi, that lady is my mom, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.48,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,Yeah. Good job recognizing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.36,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,I had a feeling it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.78,Default,Takeru,0,0,164,,I'm a genius, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:06.00,Default,Kusakabe's Sister,0,0,164,,Takeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.75,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.88,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:17.89,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,The existence of fully autonomous cursed corpses \Ncan't be made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.18,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,So they can't live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:21.60,Default,Yaga,0,0,164,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.77,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,Why're you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.02,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.06,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.11,Default,Kusakabe,0,0,164,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:37.11,Default,Assassin,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going \Nwithout your cursed corpses, Principal Yaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.91,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,To see my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:45.08,Default,Assassin,0,0,0,,Since you've been sentenced to death, \Nallow me to tell you the one way to save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:50.38,Default,Assassin,0,0,0,,Disclose how you create those fully \Nautonomous man-made cursed corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:55.13,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,You all sure grew bold \Nthe moment Satoru was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:26.62,Default,Assassin,0,0,0,,Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.71,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,I'll handle the rest. You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:31.67,Default,Assassin,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:38.38,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,You use the body's information \Nto reproduce the soul's information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:43.30,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Then you place that soul information \Nin the cursed corpse's core.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.35,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,But that alone isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:53.19,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,You have to place three highly compatible souls \Ninto a single cursed corpse, {cores housing}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:58.28,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,and have them observe each other at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:04.33,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Doing that allows the souls to stabilize \Nso self-awareness can take root.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:09.58,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Roughly three months after that, \Nit will begin supplying its own cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.12,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:14.88,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,Why tell me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.30,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't you reveal that sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.93,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,Why didn't you try to live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:26.47,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,It's a curse, Principal Gakuganji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:31.35,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,A curse from me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.11,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Masamichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.66,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,Why don't you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.54,Default,Gakuganji,0,0,0,,Do you not hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.25,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Pandas aren't bound by things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.34,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Besides, there wasn't any bad blood \Nbetween you and Masamichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:03.13,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,To me, you're just the knife \Nthat fell upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:08.47,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But remember this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:12.31,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Even pandas cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.37,Default,Tengen,0,0,0,,Hakari Kinji is currently in an \Nabandoned parking garage in Tochigi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.50,Default,Tengen,0,0,0,,running an underground fight club to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.54,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,A fight club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.00,Default,Tengen,0,0,0,,They host fist fights between sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.00,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Then the spectators are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.80,Default,Tengen,0,0,0,,Generally non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:11.26,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,That blatantly violates the secrecy \Nmandated in Article 8 of the Jujutsu Regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:15.18,Default,Tengen,0,0,0,,There may be curse users among the fighters, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.06,Default,Tengen,0,0,0,,Do be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.27,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Why are we changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.73,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Hakari{**-san} was suspended for clashing \Nwith the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.24,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,He's also actively violating jujutsu regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.95,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,If he finds out we're with Jujutsu Tech, he might run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:33.16,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,It's like we're the cops and he's the robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:34.91,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.41,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,We're on Jujutsu Tech's side now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:41.83,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,We're in the gray, \Nbut in Hakari{**-san}'s eyes, we're with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.25,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Is he even gonna help us in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.80,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.76,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Our seniors all say he's a worthless bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:52.47,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,But even Okkotsu{**-senpai} said Hakari's stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.35,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,We definitely want his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.18,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,Beat it, brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.81,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,This ain't a place for you to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.52,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,I'm gonna count to three,\Nand you'd better be on your way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.27,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,Anything else, and my fist gets involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.82,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,We need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:09.15,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Let us enter the fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.57,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,The first rule of Fight Club is:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.91,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,You do not talk about Fight Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:19.79,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,Now answer me. Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.12,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,Then, my fist gets involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.59,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Didn't get his name before I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:29.76,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,About a month ago, there was that scumbag \Nwho was all talk, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.51,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,Kondo went missing about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:35.22,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'll fill his slot for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:39.18,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Or would you rather I lay you out \Nin front of your boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.31,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:43.23,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'd be on his guard if we suddenly asked to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.98,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're not even supposed to know his name! {I guess we shouldn't know his name's Hakari.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:46.94,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I better zip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:43.81,Alt,Shrimp,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.98,Alt,Shrimp,0,0,0,,No, there's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.90,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.03,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.66,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,The boss has given you the go-ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:55.57,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,We'll pit you against today's seeded fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.62,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,However, he's the one fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.12,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.42,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itadori is better suited to the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.84,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,No go. I'll fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:09.17,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,Boss said he ain't betting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.88,Default,Shrimp,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, the deal's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.47,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Fine. We'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:19.56,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Fushiguro, that was risky. You were pushing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:20.93,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:25.60,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,If curse users are involved, \Nthere must be decent turnover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:26.94,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:28.82,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:35.16,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,If he was watching us through security cameras, \Nthere's a high chance Hakari{**-senpai} is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.95,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Itadori, you snoop around \Nfrom the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.12,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'll try to sneak into that \Nparking garage in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:41.91,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Or maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:42.96,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.96,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I think they want to see what I'm up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:50.21,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,If they catch me sneaking in, we'll lose their trust \Nand our chance to meet Hakari{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.67,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,If that happens, we'll just have to use force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.43,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Only as a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:01.14,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,We're only here to ask Hakari{**-san} \Nfor his cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:04.18,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I'd like to avoid anything that \Nmight affect relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.65,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,To be honest, I don't think \NI should be doing anything tonight. {same man} {but why does he say this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:12.86,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,But I don't want to waste what time we have \Nbefore Tsumiki's deadline. {is required to declare her participation in the Culling Game}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.90,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.61,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,it's 5 PM on the 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.07,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,That leaves us with nine days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.41,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Getting here took longer than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:29.00,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,So while I will be trying to look for Hakari{**-san} tonight, \Nif it looks risky, I'll pull out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.75,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,I hope that answers your "why not."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.63,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.38,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,There are two rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.09,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,No running away. No cursed techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.01,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.10,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I don't mind if they use cursed techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:45.64,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,Because most of the spectators \Nare non-sorcerers. They can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.48,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,If they can't see it, it won't hype them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.98,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,And the "no running" rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.61,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,It means you fight \Nwhere the spectators can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.86,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,All about the spectators, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.20,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.36,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,This is a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.45,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,What's the boss like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.83,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,Curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.79,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.04,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,You'll know if you meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:07.96,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Can I meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.34,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,There are two kinds of matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:15.67,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,Legit beat-downs like in today's tournament,\N and scripted bouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.13,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,The boss writes the scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.30,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,He might call for you \Nif you manage to shine out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.93,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,In other words, \NI just gotta put on a good show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.27,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,That makes things simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.99,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,That's your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.79,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,I was blown away \Nthe first time I saw him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.62,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.54,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,It's really all about drawing in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.50,Default,John,0,0,0,,Now, we're getting started again tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.59,Default,John,0,0,0,,It's time for the Legit Fight Club Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:01.14,Default,John,0,0,0,,Commentary will be provided by \Nyours truly, John{\fnMalgun Gothic}☆{\fn}Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:04.47,Default,John,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce tonight's exciting match-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.35,Default,John,0,0,0,,We're joined by a sudden upstart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.85,Default,John,0,0,0,,Will he rise up or burn out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:13.19,Default,John,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}It's the Dangerous Fireball Kid, Yuji Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:18.74,Default,John,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}He stands like a panda! \NHe sits like a panda! He walks like a panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.40,Default,John,0,0,0,,Pa{\alpha&HFF&}nda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.03,Default,John,0,0,0,,Pan{\alpha&HFF&}da!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:20.86,Default,John,0,0,0,,Panda{\alpha&HFF&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.82,Default,John,0,0,0,,Panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.28,Default,John,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up and place your bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.49,Default,John,0,0,0,,Everyone ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.75,Default,John,0,0,0,,Let's get ready to rumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:30.58,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I can feel the heat dying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.75,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kin{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.25,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Luck is meant to be tested, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:39.55,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,There's no thrill in betting on a sure win. {It's boring to gamble when you \Nknow who'll win from the start.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:43.59,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,There aren't many stray sorcerers \Nwho are tough enough to beat Panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.97,Default,John,0,0,0,,{\an8}Holy smokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.68,Default,John,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is the best bout in my career as a commentator!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.43,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,Looks like you might be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.68,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.48,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Did you manage to see Hakari{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.69,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.49,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,He's not on guard since we know each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.03,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,but he's avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.29,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,The other third-year's technique is also a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.26,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,You’re undercover here, right? {CR: You're hiding the fact that you're from Jujutsu Tech, right?} {it's a shame i have to put subs over this animation}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:26.97,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:29.85,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:31.77,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,You know what to do now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:38.65,Default,John,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:42.95,Default,John,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}definitely{\i0} the best bout in my career as a commentator!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.99,Default,John,0,0,0,,I've only been at this for a couple weeks, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:15.31,Default,John,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}The winner: Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.73,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,What a punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.81,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:22.99,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,The Animal Welfare Society won't stand for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.61,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Your acting sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:28.32,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Send Itadori up to the roof when the tournament's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:28.87,Default,MachoB,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.37,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,He's sure to win 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:35.75,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Plus, he's intentionally taking the fight upward \Nto impress the crowd above.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.00,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I can write a good script with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:43.76,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,And like I always say, strike while the iron's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.47,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,That's so dumb. Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:49.97,Default,Macho,0,0,0,,Got it. And what about the other brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.35,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Continue to stay sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.31,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I'll send Kirara for extra security later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.39,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.60,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a nice buzz now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:03.48,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I haven't felt this alive \Nsince my ex maxed out my credit cards.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.99,Default,Kirara,800,0,0,,Quit bringing up your ex!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.28,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:13.58,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Sounds like Itadori might make contact \Nwith Hakari after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:17.58,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Why haven't you been able to see him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.38,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Well, I do know where he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.71,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,in the monitor room on the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.13,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,but I just can't get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.01,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:30.30,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Even when I approach the door, \NI can't close the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.76,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,The sensation is similar to \NSatoru's technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.85,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I think it's because of Kirara's technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.31,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.98,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,The other third-year was a guy, right? {he asks this quesion because Kirara is a girly name} {ironic coming from a guy named Megumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.31,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Yep, a guy. {Yeah, he is/was} {since there's no indication of present/past tense, so i'm gonna try to avoid the minefield by keeping this ambiguous}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:46.69,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,So does that phenomenon only occur \Nwhen Kirara{**-san} is in the monitor room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.03,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I don't know. {they removed the line about how Hakari and Kirara are never apart}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:52.87,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I focused on being a circus panda \Ninstead of pushing too far and making them run off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.16,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I'm glad you two showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.21,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Do you think Itadori can convince him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:02.38,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,It'll be tough, but it might come down to timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:06.88,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Itadori's bright and charming personality \Nis a good match for Hakari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.97,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But we all know he sucks at lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.76,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,He doesn't just suck at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.35,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,He struggles to even see it as an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:17.56,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,So once Itadori enters the monitoring room,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:23.02,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I'll take control of the place quickly and quietly\N to buy time for the two of them to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.15,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,Um, I don't think—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.65,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll just put them to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.28,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I know where the cameras are \Nand their blind spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.11,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,How many guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:35.20,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Four at the entrance. \NTwo on each floor, except the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.16,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,We can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.58,Default,Fushiguro,0,0,0,,The only real concern is Kirara{**-san}'s technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.71,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,We can't do much about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:48.59,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,If they can warp Itadori out of there \Nor warp in some backup,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:51.09,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,we'll have to give up \Non getting through to Hakari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:53.59,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,You're still a first-year, Yu{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.89,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,You're young!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:55.64,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Yu{**-chan}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.39,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,Kin{**-chan} had to repeat a year in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.10,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You sound happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:02.73,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,Because I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.36,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,It's been a while since Kin{**-chan}'s been this hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:11.28,Default,Kirara,0,0,0,,You see, I love it when Kin{**-chan} is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.58,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:25.13,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Would you believe me if I said you could work \None hour a day and make one million yen a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.08,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:26.96,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.96,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Depends on what the work is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:35.09,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Well, for that information, \Nyou'll have to pay 200,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.05,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.35,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,I don't believe you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:43.23,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Good. Like you suspected, \Nthat's a classic con.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:49.19,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,The swindler pretends to be rich, \Nsells you a way to get rich, and takes your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:54.32,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,It's obvious if you think about it, \Nbut there's a stupid number of idiots who fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.61,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.12,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,It's all because of fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.16,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:06.08,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Both the swindler and the deceived are in \Na fever to change their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:10.17,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,People get high on fever \Nand lose sight of their judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.63,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Yet they can't even fall in love without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.64,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I love the fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:21.26,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Do you know the most direct way \Nof dealing with fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.23,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Gambling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.02,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I knew you'd get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.57,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Life is a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.65,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Loads of women have dumped me \Nbecause they hate gambling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.20,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,but they've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:45.41,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Our society tramples on those who can't bet big \Nand those who don't know when to fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:48.63,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,There isn't a single person who doesn't gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:54.05,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,What people hate isn't the gambling, \Nit's losing and being ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:57.47,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Don't some people \Njust want to live a peaceful life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.93,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I dunno anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:03.18,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I love the fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:07.69,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Fever is gambling. Gambling is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.02,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,And love is control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:15.24,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Someday, I want to control \Nthis country's fever through my Fight Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:19.78,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,With the existence of curses going public \Nand headquarters barely functioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.33,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I've got a chance to expand the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.95,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,I'm going to crush the obstacles before me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:30.38,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,and make them publicly recognize my Fight Club \Nin the coming revisions to the jujutsu regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:35.21,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'll need a strong piece on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:37.63,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.76,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Wanna get high on my fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.14,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Boss, I need to—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:00.07,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Itadori, want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.12,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm good with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:03.49,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Other than liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.41,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,What, can't handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:08.12,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,It's not that. I'm still underage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.71,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,You don't strike me as the type who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:13.84,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Did you know \NGojo Satoru can't hold his liquor, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:16.25,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Really? Who's Gojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.05,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,And I never said I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.34,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:21.22,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:32.44,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,There isn't a single sorcerer \Nwho hasn't heard of Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:34.40,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,So why did you play dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:35.73,Default,Hakari,0,0,0,,Were you...
